snippet: The duo robbinschilds wrapped up the premiere of its “I came here on my own.” at Art in General by folding it into another work, “Salzburggrubzlas, Grubzlassalzburg!”
abstract: Claudia La Rocco reviews dance piece and video installation by duo robbinschilds at Art in General.
lead_paragraph: The duo robbinschilds wrapped up the premiere of its “I came here on my own.” at Art in General by folding it into another work, “Salzburggrubzlas, Grubzlassalzburg!”
